Package: cv
Title: Code for compiling CVs from ORCID
Version: 0.6
Author: Brian O'Meara <omeara.brian@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Brian O'Meara <omeara.brian@gmail.com>
Description: Use ORCID data to create a CV. Note this uses a style sheet from Christophe-Marie Duquesne, https://github.com/mszep/pandoc_resume/blob/master/style_chmduquesne.css
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.3), scholar
SystemRequirements:
    wkhtmltopdf, pandoc
Imports:
    rorcid, RefManageR, jsonlite, knitr, rcrossref, plyr
Suggests:
    testthat
License: GPL (>=2)
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
